</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
12:56
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='765187' id='t-765187'>A friend once asked me, she said,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='766839' id='t-766839'>&quot;So when do you think this women driving will happen?&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:00
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='769590' id='t-769590'>I told her, &quot;Only if women stop asking 'When?'</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='772339' id='t-772339'>and take action to make it now.&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:06
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='775113' id='t-775113'>So it's not only about the system,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='776767' id='t-776767'>it's also about us women to drive our own life, I'd say.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:14
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='783210' id='t-783210'>So I have no clue, really, how I became an activist.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='789362' id='t-789362'>And I don't know how I became one now.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='793329' id='t-793329'>But all I know, and all I'm sure of, in the future</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='796977' id='t-796977'>when someone asks me my story,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='799745' id='t-799745'>I will say, &quot;I'm proud</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='801977' id='t-801977'>to be amongst those women who lifted the ban,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='804833' id='t-804833'>fought the ban, and celebrated everyone's freedom.&quot;</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:39
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='808608' id='t-808608'>So the question I started my talk with,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='811905' id='t-811905'>who do you think is more difficult to face,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='815105' id='t-815105'>oppressive governments or oppressive societies?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='818062' id='t-818062'>I hope you find clues to answer that from my speech.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:51
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='820961' id='t-820961'>Thank you, everyone.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
13:53
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='822417' id='t-822417'>(Applause)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='827185' id='t-827185'>Thank you.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='830309' id='t-830309'>(Applause)</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='835993' id='t-835993'>Thank you. (Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
